text:
Hello all! On behalf of the team behind the Mobile Chat SDK, I want to check in to see how you've been finding your in-app customer service experience so far.

My teammates and I are always looking for ways to improve the SDK, and we would love to hear your feedback. Please consider filling out <https://forms.gle/TSHKawfhGZJmgrUa6|this form> at your convenience. We'll do our best to carefully consider each and every feedback. Thank you. :slightly_smiling_face:
